## üñ±Ô∏è Main Browser Commands

| Command | Purpose | Example |
|---------|---------|---------|
| `@browser navigate <url>` | Open a webpage | `@browser navigate https://google.com` |
| `@browser click <selector>` | Click button/link | `@browser click #login` |
| `@browser type <selector> <text>` | Type in field | `@browser type input[name=email] test@example.com` |
| `@browser scroll <direction>` | Scroll page | `@browser scroll down` |
| `@browser screenshot` | Capture current screen | `@browser screenshot` |
| `@browser console` | Read console logs | `@browser console` |
| `@browser network` | Check network requests | `@browser network` |

