## üß† Smart Features

- **Auto-detects local servers**: Knows if dev apps are running (e.g., `localhost:3000`, `localhost:4200`)
- **Efficient logs**: Reads only relevant lines (saves tokens)
- **Visual feedback**: Uses screenshots to "see" UI and detect issues
- **Accessibility checks**: Test contrast, ARIA labels, alt text

