## üîí Security & Approval Settings

**Recommended**: Keep **Manual Approval** mode ON for safety.

Browser actions require approval by default. Configure in:
- **Cursor Settings** ‚Üí **Chat** ‚Üí **Auto-Run**

**Available modes**:
- **Manual approval** (recommended): Review each action
- **Allow-listed actions**: Auto-run trusted actions
- **Auto-run**: All actions execute immediately (use with caution)

**‚ö†Ô∏è Never use auto-run with untrusted code or unfamiliar websites.**

